Spent about nine months there. We repatriated the 
Japanese army, got them all disarmed. Primarily

08:08.043 --> 08:16.952
the concern was that when the Chinese learned that 
the war was over that they would massacre the whole

08:08.043 --> 08:16.952
army. There was not a great big number of Japanese 
there because they had all the arms and so forth. We

08:23.699 --> 08:48.576
repatriated them out of there, and by that time, 
