took 18 hours, which was the norm. Describe a 
typical class day's routine. Got up at what hour

20:16.610 --> 20:18.912
and did what all? Well, first thing, we had a mess 
hall where we ate. And they had hours for

20:27.400 --> 20:33.067
breakfast, so if you wanted breakfast, you had to 
get there by 7 o'clock, I think. But we were all used

20:33.267 --> 20:39.115
to that anyway from the background, so that wasn't 
really a problem for anyone. And we had no

20:39.816 --> 20:41.898
transportation. There was, in our group, in fact, 
in our group, these were sort of in clusters of

20:41.918 --> 20:53.593
those tar paper shacks. about four or five in each 
one, and I think in our cluster there was one

20:53.978 --> 21:01.746
automobile and one motorcycle. That was a total 
transportation system. But we'd get up, go to

21:04.829 --> 21:07.532
breakfast. There were not bugle calls or anything 
